    <p><strong>Pastor Jason Kamotho</strong> has been a guiding light in our lives and a true shepherd of our spiritual
      community. He have dedicated his life to spreading the message of love, compassion,
      and faith.</p>

    <p>Throughout his tenure, Pastor Kamotho has shown an unwavering commitment to The Potters house. [He/She/They] have
      not only led us in prayer but also provided a source of strength,
      wisdom, and support during both joyful and challenging times.</p>

    <p>One of the qualities that make Pastor Kamotho exceptional is his wisdom, which has
      inspired us to become better individuals. His teachings resonate with warmth and sincerity,
      creating a sense of unity within our congregation.</p>

    <img src="pic2.jpg" alt="Pastor Jason Kamotho">

    <p>This tribute is a token of our gratitude for the tireless efforts, compassion, and leadership that Pastor has
